      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="When a material has been produced in a production/process run, a Goods Receipt for the order must be posted. A Goods Receipt is the physical acceptance of an item into a stocking location. In a repetitive manufacturing environment, this may be the final backflushing point (milestone). "/>
